id: pm-7d3m
title: Stabilize post-release cross-platform CI tests
description: Fix macOS and Windows CI regressions from post-release workflow run 25210023872 without moving the published 2026.5.1 release tag.
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[5]: ci,cross-platform,pm-cli,release,tests
