acceptance_criteria: "Main-branch CI passes on Linux, macOS, and Windows after focused cross-platform test fixes; changed files and verification are linked; release tag v2026.5.1 remains published at the verified release commit."
parent: pm-3fti
comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-01T10:01:56.427Z",codex-release-agent,"Duplicate check before create: pm context --limit 10 showed active parent pm-3fti plus tracker hygiene only; pm search 'windows macos ci path signal fixture' returned closed historical CI work only; pm list-open/list-in-progress found no active CI hardening item. Net-new issue is required for GitHub Actions run 25210023872 failures."
  "2026-05-01T10:12:42.617Z",codex-release-agent,"Implemented cross-platform CI hardening: files discover and validate now compare canonical real paths for containment while preserving stable output; Windows-sensitive tests no longer depend on shell-only quoting or exact temp-path aliases. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- failed CI suites passed 5 files/149 tests; pnpm typecheck passed; git diff --check passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 81 files/1087 tests with 100% coverage; pm test pm-7d3m --run --progress passed linked test."
  "2026-05-01T10:34:03.379Z",codex-release-agent,"Follow-up after GitHub Actions run 25210786166: Windows still failed only the nested run-tests integration smoke. Updated scripts/run-tests.mjs to invoke Vitest through node_modules/vitest/vitest.mjs instead of nested pnpm exec, and added assertion diagnostics for future failures. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/run-tests-script.integration.spec.ts passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- failed CI suites passed 5 files/149 tests; pnpm typecheck passed; git diff --check passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 81 files/1087 tests with 100% coverage; pm test pm-7d3m --run --progress passed linked test."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-01T10:01:56.427Z",codex-release-agent,Do not move or republish v2026.5.1 for test-only CI hardening after release publication.
